            <h1>How It Works</h1>
            <p class="lead">CivicConnect makes it easy for citizens to communicate with their representatives through a simple, intuitive platform.</p>
            <ol class="text-left">
                <li><strong>Sign Up:</strong> Citizens, politicians, and moderators sign up and get verified to join the platform.</li>
                <li><strong>Report Issues:</strong> Citizens report local issues and concerns, which can then be viewed by politicians and moderators.</li>
                <li><strong>Response & Updates:</strong> Politicians respond to issues, post updates, and engage in discussions with citizens.</li>
                <li><strong>Moderation:</strong> Moderators ensure that interactions remain respectful and constructive by monitoring discussions.</li>
                <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> All actions are tracked, ensuring transparency and accountability.</li>
            </ol>
        </div>
